rows.label: qst200602_msg0002
rows.name:
You mean that huge monster
I saw the other day?

rows.label: qst200602_msg0004
rows.name:
Actually, it was so out there that
nobody believes me when I tell 'em.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0005
rows.name:
Early in the morning... I think
it was around 5 o'clock.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0006
rows.name:
On a hill near the Isle of the
Three Swords, I saw a huge shadow
moving in the Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0007
rows.name: Man, I doubted my own eyes at first.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0008
rows.name:
I never thought a monster
that huge could exist.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0009
rows.name:
Anyway, if you're going to
investigate, you should be careful.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0010
rows.name:
I don't know if even a
Divine Beast warship could
take down that monster.
